H1.text: Which late English singer released albums entitled ‘Frank’ and ‘Back to Black’. Kate Nash

H2.text: Which late English singer released albums entitled ‘Frank’ and ‘Back to Black’. Paloma Faith

H3.text: Which late English singer released albums entitled ‘Frank’ and ‘Back to Black’. Winehouse

A4.text: Winehouse's debut studio album, Frank (2003), was commercially successful in the UK and drew critical acclaim for its mature songwriting and jazz-imbued production.

A5.text: Her second studio album, Back to Black (2006), was an international critical and commercial success, and became one of the best-selling albums of all time.
